,000 children and youth </div><div class="t m7cb x3 h4 y1b97 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are now enjoying the benefits of Christian </div><div class="t m5eb x3 h4 y1f9e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">education. </div><div class="t mf4e x27 h4 y1d12 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;In all this,&quot; wrote the editor of the New  </div><div class="t m1d4 x5a h4 y29c3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">York </div><div class="t m442 x9f h30 y2a21 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Independent, </div><div class="t mb90 x67 h4 y299f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">August 23, 1915, &quot;Ellen </div><div class="t m1b0e x5a h4 y29bf ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">G. White has been the inspiration and </div><div class="t mab6 x1c h4 y29c4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">guide. . . . She lived the life and did the </div><div class="t ma35 x5a h4 y2a22 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">work of a worthy prophetess.&quot; </div><div class="t m28d8 x7 h4 y1d25 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. What timely counsel given in </div><div class="t mc6f x1c h4 y23bd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ancient times is most appropriate for </div><div class="t m2b42 x1c h4 y2195 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s remnant people of today? 2 </div><div class="t m150 x1c h4 y203f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Chron. 20:20. </div><div class="t m1080 x56 h4 y18d8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—As heralds of the everlasting gos-</div><div class="t ma7 x1c h4 y1aad ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pel this people bear the distinguishing cre-</div><div class="t m6be x1c h4 y1ee8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dentials of the remnant church, endeavor-</div><div class="t m1ff x1c h4 y1e57 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing to keep all the commandments of God </div><div class="t ma8a x1c h4 y1765 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and possessing the testimony of Jesus. </div><div class="t mde8 x1c h4 y1c57 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Truly, &quot;We have nothing to fear for the </div><div class="t m70a x1c h4 y1cf8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">future, except as we shall forget the way </div><div class="t m5d0 x1c 